Upstream-Name: libgcrypt
Source: https://gnupg.org/software/libgcrypt/
Comment:
 This Debian packaging is adapted from the Ubuntu and Debian libgcrypt20
 packaging shipped for libgcrypt 1.10.3. The Rust port in this repository
 keeps the upstream ABI, helper tools, and maintainer-script payload expected
 by downstream Ubuntu 24.04 consumers.

